description: This is an entry point file for a React-based frontend application. It imports the React library, ReactDOM for rendering, a CSS stylesheet, and the main App component. It initializes the React app by rendering the App component into the DOM element with id 'root' within a StrictMode wrapper.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering the app into a DOM container.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the root DOM node.
